                                        <h2 class="art-postheader"><a href="./node/1093.html" title="The Muslim World League calls upon the leaders of the Nation and the International Organizations to save the Syrian people from Genocide">The Muslim World League calls upon the leaders of the Nation and the International Organizations to save the Syrian people from Genocide</a></h2>
                                    </div>
                                                
                <div class="art-postcontent art-postcontent-0 clearfix"><div class="art-article">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><div><u>Makkah</u></div>
<div>The Muslim World League calls upon the leaders of the Muslim Ummah, the Organization of Islamic Cooperation, the Arab League, the United Nation, the UN Security Council and Human rights organizations around the world to come to the rescue of the people of Syria, who are the victims of continuous bloody massacres never witnessed before.</div>
<div>The following statement is issued by His Excellency the Secretary General of the Muslim World League, Dr. Abdullah Bin Abdelmohsin Al-Turki:</div></div></div></div>  </div>
</div>
